name: DAIC 2020 Best Digital Assets Media Award by Stobox

metadata.name: DAIC 2020 "Best Digital Assets Media Award" by Stobox
metadata.description:
This NFT is an interplay of two cutting-edge technologies - machine creativity and digital collectible.
The background for this image is created by the AI. It is generated from pure randomness and, therefore, unique. 
Blockchain makes the intangible value of this token accessible, transferable, and eternal. 
It is a gift to brave media fighting through the noise of politics and entertainment to inform the world about what really matters.
